<h2><a name='sect0' href='#toc0'>Name</a></h2>
<b>MPI_Comm_size </b> - Returns the size of the group associated with
a communicator.
<p>
<h2><a name='sect1' href='#toc1'>Syntax</a></h2>

<h2><a name='sect2' href='#toc2'>C Syntax</a></h2>
<br>
<pre>#include &lt;mpi.h&gt;
int MPI_Comm_size(MPI_Comm comm, int *size)
</pre>
<h2><a name='sect3' href='#toc3'>Fortran Syntax</a></h2>
<br>
<pre>INCLUDE &rsquo;mpif.h&rsquo;
MPI_COMM_SIZE(COMM, SIZE, IERROR)
<tt> </tt>&nbsp;<tt> </tt>&nbsp;INTEGER<tt> </tt>&nbsp;<tt> </tt>&nbsp;COMM, SIZE, IERROR
</pre>
<h2><a name='sect4' href='#toc4'>C++ Syntax</a></h2>
<br>
<pre>#include &lt;mpi.h&gt;
int Comm::Get_size() const
</pre>
<h2><a name='sect5' href='#toc5'>Input Parameter</a></h2>

<dl>

<dt>comm </dt>
<dd>Communicator (handle).
<p> </dd>
</dl>

<h2><a name='sect6' href='#toc6'>Output Parameters</a></h2>

<dl>

<dt>size </dt>
<dd>Number
of processes in the group of comm (integer). </dd>

